</p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-btwLGw cuLvxI pf-52_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-53_ pf-text-1"><strong>Accessibility</strong> - Learners can access updated content anytime and anywhere, accommodating varied schedules.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-55_ pf-text-1"><strong>Cost-effectiveness</strong> - Reduces the need for travel and physical materials, lowering the cost of training.


























































</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-57_ pf-text-1"><strong>Tailored learning</strong> - Offers courses that cater to individual learning paces and styles.



























































</li></ul></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-59_ pf-r pf-c-lm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fatbYi lnCFtg pf-60_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cXPBhi kkWDYP pf-61_ pf-heading-1-h3">Incorporating best practices</h3><p class="sc-edLa-Dd hZPWCc pf-63_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Best practices in designing e-learning for AHPs include:


</p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-btwLGw cuLvxI pf-65_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-66_ pf-text-1"><strong>Interactive content</strong> - Engages learners and enhances retention through multimedia, quizzes, and simulations.&nbsp;</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-68_ pf-text-1"><strong>Peer collaboration</strong> - Encourages knowledge exchange through forums and group activities.



























































